def getCurrencyData(currency, _from, _to):
  page = requests.get('https://cbr.ru/currency_base/dynamics/?UniDbQuery.Posted=True&UniDbQuery.mode=1&UniDbQuery.date_req1=&UniDbQuery.date_req2=&UniDbQuery.VAL_NM_RQ=' + currencies[currency] + "&UniDbQuery.From=" + _from + "&UniDbQuery.To=" + _to)
  soup = BeautifulSoup(page.content, 'html.parser')
  table =  soup.find_all("table")
  if (len(table) == 0): # Если данных нет
    return None
  else:                 # Усли данные нашлись    
    th = soup.find_all("th")
    td = soup.find_all("td")
    del td[0] # Удаляем название валюты за ненадобностью
    df = pd.DataFrame(columns=[th[0].contents[0], th[1].contents[0], currency]) # Создали датасет с нужными колонками
    i = 0
    while (i <= len(td)-1): # парсим таблицу
      data= []
      for k in range(3):
        data += td[i:i+3][k].contents
      df.loc[len(df.index)] = [data[0], data[1], data[2]]
      i = i+3

    df[currency] =  df[currency].apply(lambda x : str(x).replace(",", "."))
    df[currency] =  df[currency].astype("float") / df[df.columns[1]].astype("float")
    df[df.columns[1]] = 1
    return df

def getData(date_from, date_to, *args):
  if (len(args) == 1):
    return getCurrencyData(args[0], date_from, date_to)
  else: 
    current_df = None
    for arg in range(len(args)):
      tmp = getCurrencyData(args[arg], date_from, date_to)
      if (tmp is None):
        continue
      else:
        if (arg != 0):
          current_df = pd.merge(tmp, current_df, on=["Дата", "Единиц"])
        else: 
          current_df = tmp
    return current_df

scaler = StandardScaler()
for col in data.columns:
  data[col] = scaler.fit_transform(data[col].values.reshape(-1, 1))


def plots(x):
  fig = plt.figure(figsize=(30,10))
  ax_1 = fig.add_subplot(1, 3, 1)
  ax_2 = fig.add_subplot(1, 3, 2)
  ax_3 = fig.add_subplot(1, 3, 3)
  
  # distribution plot
  fig1 = sns.distplot(x, fit=stats.norm, kde=False,bins=50, ax=ax_1)
  # Q-Q
  pplot = sm.ProbPlot(x)
  fig2 = pplot.qqplot(line="r", ax=ax_2)

  # P-P
  pplot = sm.ProbPlot(x)
  fig3 = pplot.ppplot(line="r", ax=ax_3)
  plt.show()

for col in data.columns:
  plots(data[col])

def central_stat(x):
  plt.figure(figsize=(10,5))

  sns.distplot(x, fit=stats.norm, kde=False, bins=50)

  plt.axvline(st.mean(x), 0, 1, label='Среднее', color='red')
  plt.axvline(st.median(x), 0, 1, label='Медиана', color='blue')
  plt.axvline(stats.mode(x)[0], 0, 1, label='Мода', color='black')

  plt.legend(fontsize=16)
  plt.show()

for col in data.columns:
    central_stat(data[col])

def print_info(x):
  print("---------",x.to_frame().columns[0],"---------")
  print("Среднее: ", st.mean(x))
  print("Медиана: ", st.median(x))
  print("Мода: ", stats.mode(x)[0])
  print("\n")

def create_norm(x):
  loc, scale = stats.norm.fit(x)
  n = stats.norm(loc=loc, scale=scale)
  return n

for col in data.columns:
    print("---------",data[col].to_frame().columns[0],"---------")

    print("Тест Андерсона-Дарлинга для RUB:", stats.anderson(data[col], 'norm'))
    print("Тест Шапиро-Уилка для RUB:", stats.shapiro(data[col]), "\n")

def crop(df, column, left=0.05, right=0.95):
    left = df[column].quantile(left)
    right = df[column].quantile(right)
    return df[(df[column] > left) & (df[column] < right)].copy(deep=True)

for col in data.columns:
  data = crop(data, col)

print("\n-------Чистые данные-------")
print(data.describe())

def show_criteria(label, method, x, y):
  criteria_val, criteria_p = method(data[x],data[y])
  print(label, " R =", criteria_val, "    | p= ", criteria_p)

for ind1 in range(len(data.columns)):
  if (ind1 == len(data.columns)-1):
    ind2 = 0
  else:
    ind2 = ind1 + 1
  print("--", data.columns[ind1], "--", data.columns[ind2], "--")
  show_criteria("Kendall correlation: ", stats.kendalltau, data.columns[ind1], data.columns[ind2])
  show_criteria("Pearson correlation: ", stats.pearsonr, data.columns[ind1], data.columns[ind2])
  show_criteria("Spearman correlation: ", stats.spearmanr, data.columns[ind1], data.columns[ind2])
  print("\n")

def show_regression(x, y, axis):
  axis.scatter(data[x] ,data[y])
  m, b = np. polyfit(data[x], data[y], 1)
  axis.plot(data[x], m*data[x]+b)

fig, ax = plt.subplots(1, len(data.columns), figsize=(20,10))


for ind1 in range(len(data.columns)):
  if (ind1 == len(data.columns)-1):
    ind2 = 0
  else:
    ind2 = ind1 + 1
  show_regression( data.columns[ind1], data.columns[ind2], ax[ind1])
